  **Output:**

  ```json
  {"title": "Vessel", "score": 5.373150825500488}
  {"title": "Boats", "score": 4.589139938354492}
  {"title": "And the Ship Sails On", "score": 4.3452959060668945}
  {"title": "Broken Vessels", "score": 4.3452959060668945}
